definition.value: Catalysis of the eliminative degradation of polysaccharides containing 1,4-beta-D-hexosaminyl and 1,3-beta-D-glucuronosyl or 1,3-alpha-L-iduronosyl linkages to disaccharides containing 4-deoxy-beta-D-gluc-4-enuronosyl groups.
Catalysis of the reaction -  4-(4-deoxy-alpha-D-gluc-4-enuronosyl)-D-galacturonate -eq- 2 5-dehydro-4-deoxy-D-glucuronate.

Catalysis of the eliminative cleavage of polysaccharides containing 1,4-linked D-glucuronate or L-iduronate residues and 1,4-alpha-linked 2-sulfoamino-2-deoxy-6-sulfo-D-glucose residues to give oligosaccharides with terminal 4-deoxy-alpha-D-gluc-4-enuronosyl groups at their nonreducing ends.

Catalysis of the reaction -  a pectate -eq- a pectate + 4-(4-deoxy-alpha-D-galact-4-enuronosyl)-D-galacturonate. This reaction is the eliminative cleavage of 4-(4-deoxy-alpha-D-galact-4-enuronosyl)-D-galacturonate from the reducing end of pectate, i.e. de-esterified pectin.

Catalysis of the reaction -  a pectin -eq- an oligosaccharide with 4-deoxy-6-O-methyl-alpha-D-galact-4-enuronate end + a pectin. This reaction is the eliminative cleavage of (1--gt-4)-alpha-D-galacturonan methyl ester to give oligosaccharides with 4-deoxy-6-O-methyl-alpha-D-galact-4-enuronosyl groups at their nonreducing ends.

Catalysis of the reaction -  polysaccharides containing a terminal alpha-L-guluronate group -eq- oligosaccharides with 4-deoxy-alpha-L-erythro-hex-4-enuronosyl end. This reaction is the eliminative cleavage of polysaccharides containing a terminal a-L-guluronate group, to give oligopolysaccharides with 4-deoxy-a-L-erythro-hex-4-enuronosyl groups at their nonreducing ends.

Catalysis of the reaction -  xanthan -eq- oligosaccharide with 4-deoxy-alpha-L-threo-hex-4-enuronosyl end + pyruvylate mannose. This reaction is the eliminative cleavage of the terminal beta-D-mannosyl-beta-D-1,4-glucuronosyl linkage of the side-chain of the polysaccharide xanthan, leaving a 4-deoxy-alpha-L-threo-hex-4-enuronosyl group at the terminus of the side-chain.
Catalysis of the reaction -  CDP-choline + ceramide -eq- CMP + H(+) + sphingomyelin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-serine + CDP-ethanolamine -eq- L-serine-phosphoethanolamine + CMP + H(+).
Catalysis of the transfer of a glycerophospho group from one membrane-derived oligosaccharide to another.
Catalysis of the reaction -  phosphatidylcholine + H2O -eq- 1-acylglycerophosphocholine + a carboxylate. This reaction requires Ca2+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  phosphatidylcholine + H2O -eq- 1-acylglycerophosphocholine + a carboxylate. This reaction does not require Ca2+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (+)-borneol + NAD(+) -eq- (1R, 4R)-camphor + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (+)-neomenthol + NADP(+) -eq- (2S,5R)-menthone + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (+)-cis-sabinol + NAD(+) -eq- (1S,5S)-sabinone + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (-)-borneol + NAD(+) -eq- (1S,4S)-camphor + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (-)-menthol + NADP(+) -eq- (2S,5R)-menthone + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (-)-menthol + H(+) + NADPH + O(2) -eq- 1,4-menthane-3,8-diol + H(2)O + NADP(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + dAMP -eq- ADP + dADP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + deoxynucleoside phosphate -eq- ADP + deoxynucleoside diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (R)-citramalate -eq- 2-methylmaleate + H(2)O.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (R)-4-dehydropantoate + H(2)O + NAD(+) -eq- (R)-3,3-dimethylmalate + 2 H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-citramalate -eq- H(2)O + mesaconate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-methylmalonyl-CoA + H(2)O -eq- CoA + H(+) + methylmalonate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S,S)-butane-2,3-diol + NAD(+) -eq- acetoin + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  H2O + methyl-2-alpha-L-fucopyranosyl-beta-D-galactoside -eq- L-fucose + methyl beta-D-galactoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  [(1--gt-3)-beta-D-glucosyl](n) + phosphate -eq- [(1--gt-3)-beta-D-glucosyl](n-1) + alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate -  substrates include laminarin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  [oligomeric (1--gt-3)-beta-D-glucosyl](n) + phosphate -eq- [(1--gt-3)-beta-D-glucosyl](n-1) + alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  propane-1,3-diol + NAD+ -eq- 3-hydroxypropanal + NADH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-D-xylose + [(1--gt-4)-beta-D-xylan](n) -eq- UDP + [(1--gt-4)-beta-D-xylan](n+1).
Catalysis of the reaction -  1-methyladenosine + H(2)O -eq- 1-methyladenine + ribofuranose.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (-)-quinate + pyrroloquinoline-quinone -eq- (-)-3-dehydroquinate + pyrroloquinoline-quinol.
Catalysis of the reaction -  11-cis-retinyl palmitate + H(2)O -eq- 11-cis-retinol + H(+) + palmitate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3alpha,7alpha,12beta-trihydroxy-5beta-cholanate + NADP(+) -eq- 3alpha,7alpha-dihydroxy-12-oxo-5beta-cholanate + H(+) + NADPH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  (5Z)-(15S)-11-alpha-hydroxy-9,15-dioxoprostanoate + NAD(P)+ --gt- (5Z)-(15S)-11-alpha-hydroxy-9,15-dioxoprosta-13-enoate + NAD(P)H + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  16-alpha-hydroxysteroid -eq- 16-beta-hydroxysteroid.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2'-hydroxydihydrodaidzein + NADP+ -eq- 2'-hydroxydaidzein + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  vestitone + NADP+ -eq- 2'-hydroxyformononetin + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + 2,3-dihydroxybenzoate + L-serine -eq- products of ATP breakdown + N-(2,3-dihydroxybenzoyl)-L-serine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,3-dihydroxyindole + O(2) -eq- anthranilate + CO(2) + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  (2R,3S)-2,3-dimethylmalate -eq- propanoate + pyruvate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,4-diaminopentanoate + H2O + NAD(P)+ -eq- 2-amino-4-oxopentanoate + NH3 + NAD(P)H + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + ornithine -eq- 5-amino-2-oxopentanoate + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,5-dioxopiperazine + H(2)O -eq- glycylglycine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2,5-dioxopentanoate + NADP+ + H2O -eq- 2-oxoglutarate + NADPH + H+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-acetolactate -eq- 3-hydroxy-3-methyl-2-oxobutanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-butyne-1,4-diol + NAD(+) -eq- 4-hydroxy-2-butynal + H(+) + NADH.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + L-2-aminoadipate -eq- 2-oxoadipate + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-2-aminohexanoate + 2-oxoglutarate -eq- 2-oxohexanoate + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-carboxy-D-arabinitol 1-phosphate + H(2)O -eq- 2-carboxy-D-arabinitol + phosphate.
